807
00:37:43,199 --> 00:37:43,340
Andrea.

808
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:43,760
Andrea.

809
00:37:45,465 --> 00:37:46,525
Dai, sta uscendo.

810
00:37:46,606 --> 00:37:49,568
Eccolo, guarda che bel bambino.

811
00:37:49,809 --> 00:37:50,269
Andrea.

812
00:37:50,510 --> 00:37:51,690
Andrea.

